text: Mohamed Guezzaz () (born October 1, 1962) is a retired football (soccer) referee from Morocco, best known for supervising match Spain-Slovenia during the 2002 FIFA World Cup. ==References== * Profile at worldfootball.net Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:Moroccan football referees Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:2002 FIFA World Cup referees
title: Mohamed Guezzaz
